### User register
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### User login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Get profile (replace TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Create trip (replace TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:8082/trips
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pickup_lat": 10.75,
  "pickup_lng": 106.66,
  "dropoff_lat": 10.78,
  "dropoff_lng": 106.70
}

### Cancel trip (replace ID + TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:8082/trips/ID/cancel
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Estimate payment directly
POST http://localhost:3004/payments/estimate
Content-Type: application/json

{ "distance_km": 5 }
